	(text "NAME			|	GPIO	| DESC. \nBOOT			|	00		| BOOT mode, button\nLED_IO01		|	01		| LED, Indication, --debug\nBZ_IO02		|	02		| Buzzer, Indication --debug\nSTRAP			|	03		| STRAPPING PIN, DO NOT CONNECT\nBTN_IO04		|	04		| Button, INPUT_PULLPIT needed\nBTN_IO05		|	05	 	| Button, INPUT_PULLPIT needed\nPH_L			|	06		| \nEN_L			|	07		| \nEN_R			|	08		| \ncSelect0		|	09		| \ncSelect1		|	10		| \nD_EXT1			|	11		| \nD_EXT2			|	12    	| \nD_EXT3			|	13		| \nMODE_SW		|	14		| \nRESET_SW		|	15		| \nRESET_SW		|	16		|\nRESET_SW		|	17		|\nRESET_SW		|	18    	|\nD-				|	19		| USB data-\nD+				|	20		| USB data+\nNC				|	21		| NOT CONNECTED, FREE\nNC				|	35		| NOT CONNECTED, FREE\nRESET_SW		|	36		|\nRESET_SW		|	37		|\nRESET_SW		|	38		|\nACC_INT  		|	39		| Gyroscope pin interrupt\nGYR_INT		|	40		|\nSCL				|	41		| I2C, data SCL line\nSDA				|	42		| I2C, data SDA line\nLED_IO47		|	43		| (DEFAULT UART-TX)LED, Indication, --debug\nLED_IO44		|	44		| (DEFAULT UART-RX)LED, Indication, --debug (BUG, WRONG PIN NUM.)\nSTRAP			|	45		| STRAPPING PIN, DO NOT CONNECT\nSTRAP			|	46		| STRAPPING PIN, DO NOT CONNECT\nNC		  		|	47		| NOT CONNECTED, FREE\nNC				|	48		| NOT CONNECTED, FREE"
